Invocation Name: got your six t. v.
des:
Become the Go-To digital platform for today’s top business headlines and go behind the headlines for the personal stories impacting Veterans, Active Duty and Military Spouses. GotUrSix TV aggregates all the top business headlines of the day and talk with Entrepreneurs, Influencers, VSOs, Business Executives, and Government Officials who share their journey of service, sacrifice and business expertise. 
The GOTURSIX TV skill allows the user to listen to headlines. this can either be the latest headlines or headlines by category. it also allows the user to list to an article by saying the specific headline
